5000|$|In 2001, Fox News Channel's The Edge, psychic Sylvia Browne {{said that}} she knew where the body of <b>Chandra</b> <b>Levy</b> was located. On Fox News Channel's Judith Regan Tonight, psychic James Van Praagh {{discussed}} <b>Chandra</b> <b>Levy.</b> Shine responded to questions about having psychics appear on Fox News Channel by saying that psychics are [...] "part of the story" [...] because the Levy family had consulted some. Shine said that the psychics provide [...] "another opinion, another side of the story".|$|E
